description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys along with Jarobi of A Tribe Called Quest, AP the Jeweler and the D.C. family talk current events and recent 25th anniversaries of Tribe and Wu-Tang albums.
